quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  76,1,"Was there a period of time when man was not even worthy of a mention?",footnotes:182460:1
  76,2,"Verily We created man out of a drop of intermingled sperm so that We might try him, and We therefore endowed him with hearing and sight.",footnotes:182461:1,footnotes:182462:2,footnotes:182463:3
  76,3,"Surely We showed him the Right Path, regardless of whether he chooses to be thankful or unthankful (to his Lord).",footnotes:182464:1
  76,4,"For the unbelievers, We have kept ready chains and fetters and a Blazing Fire."
  76,5,"The virtuous shall drink from a cup tempered with camphor water.",footnotes:182465:1